title: Quentin Unchained (Tarantino soundtrack compilation)
description:
A collection of tracks from Quentin Tarantino soundtracks.

Six tracks from Reservoir Dogs (5, 6, 8, 9, 16, and 25), seven from Pulp Fiction (2, 7, 11, 12, 15, 19, and 26), three from Jackie Brown (1, 18, and 20), four from the Kill Bills (3, 10, 21, and 22), two from Death Proof (14 and 23), one from Inglourious Basterds (17), and three from Django Unchained (tracks 4, 13, and 24).
